headline: Xcel Energy Inc. Board Declares Dividend on Common Stock
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, May 21, 2025--The Board of Directors of Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) today declared a quarterly dividend on its common stock of 57 cents per share. The dividends are payable July 20, 2025, to shareholders of record on June 13, 2025.
